text.tspan: * TILT GRAVITY AND/OR ROTATE TILE TO DIVERT CRITTER

* DRAG CRITTER TILE WITHOUT LOOSING IT
* SPAWN A NEW TILE HERE (COST SUBSTANTIAL OF GAINED CREDITS)
